<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
  US Letter (8.5 x 11 in). Drawn to-scale relative to other paper drawables in
  this directory; all share viewport 400x400 and use the same scale factor
  (360 units = longest side of Tabloid = 17 in -> 21.18 units/inch).
  Letter therefore renders at 180 x 232.9 units, centered.

  Includes a small filled star at top-right as the "this is the size most
  people in North America want" affordance (referenced by the
  PaperSizeCard tooltip in MainActivity).
-->
